{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1723293399.307047", "card_id": "Q_663791142", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 823}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "两研究生午休在工作室用工作电脑打游戏被重罚，需完成双倍毕业成果才可答辩，导师被罚款，学校处理是否合理？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "8 月 8 日，一则广东工业大学两名研究生因午休打游戏遭重罚的帖子引发关注。该网帖显示，该校光研院两名研一学生在工作室午休期间，利用工位电脑打游戏、观看游戏视频，被给予多项处罚：被严重警告且通报批评；需达到毕业成果数量要求的两倍才能申请答辩；导师被罚 2000 元等。 潇湘晨报记者了解到，该网帖中的「光研院」系该校信息工程学院的先进光子技术研究院（筹）。8 月 8 日下午，潇湘晨报记者联系到该校信息工程学院，工作人员表示，已经关注到此事，确实是学院发生的事，学院已经有老师在处理此事了，「具体情况不太清楚。」两名研究生午休时在工作室打游戏被重罚？校方回应"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-06c6768d493cfe9546e9a3c047e52155_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "704 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/663791142"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIkJql8YGDz8VNEAMaCTEwOTc4NjgzMiDGotO1BjAAOLYNQAByCTY2Mzc5MTE0MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1723293399.308216", "card_id": "Q_663911064", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 223}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "7 月小米 SU7 销量超越特斯拉登顶第一，如何看待这一成绩？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "[图片]"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-8a05c7a33aea77ce6fa8933c95d7c142_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "474 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/663911064"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIkJql8YGDz8VNEAMaCTEwOTgxMzQ3NCD0k9u1BjAAOKMDQAFyCTY2MzkxMTA2NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1723293399.308575", "card_id": "Q_663873